profile: We have been in the piano moving business for over 11 years now and although we are located in the Ottawa/Gatineau area we service the provinces of Ontario and Quebec on a regular basis. We specialize in piano moving but have launched a moving division that can handle just about any item that needs to be relocated. We also offer piano storage for our clients that are between homes or having renovations done. Recently we were recognized by the Canadian Business Review Board Inc for Outstanding Service, Customer Satisfaction, Business Leadership and Strong Vision.
